{"actor":"agent:claude-opus-4-reviewer","data":{"body":"Reviewed diff bf31f23 cold. One-attribute fix: crossorigin=\"anonymous\" added to all 8 webp banner preloads, AVIF preload correctly left without it (verified in dist/index.html: 8 banner preloads have crossorigin, AVIF has none). Root cause is correct \u2014 THREE.Loader defaults crossOrigin='anonymous' (three@0.183), so TextureLoader's CORS-mode request now matches the preload and is consumed instead of re-fetched. typecheck + build pass. Same-origin CORS-mode needs no ACAO header, so no server change required. The remaining runtime check (8 webp requests not 16, served-from-preload) needs a throttled browser, but the mechanism is well-understood. PASS.","role":"review"},"id":"ev_01KTT29XPY2Q633CQQ51Q10N0A","schema_version":1,"task_id":"task_01KTT26KV75GY7VM7P83VC8NR3","ts":"2026-06-11T00:46:21Z","type":"comment_added"}
